name: Fidelity Tactical High Income Fund
longDescription: The Fund invests primarily in a mix of income-producing securities which may be located anywhere in the world. It can invest in these securities either directly or indirectly through investments in underlying funds. A diversified income solution that can offer the potential for enhanced yield.
